Package: secubox-homeassistant
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, secubox-core (>= 1.0), python3-uvicorn | python3-pip, python3-httpx | python3-pip
Recommends: docker.io | podman, lxc
Description: Home Assistant IoT Hub for SecuBox
 Debian bookworm port of Home Assistant integration module.
 Provides FastAPI backend on /api/v1/homeassistant/ via Unix socket.
 .
 Features:
  - Docker/Podman/LXC container management for Home Assistant
  - Entity and device browser with controls
  - Automation management with enable/disable toggles
  - Scene management and activation
  - HACS (Home Assistant Community Store) integration
  - Backup and restore functionality
  - CRT-light P31 phosphor theme with HA blue accents
